      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks for the breakdown. You mentioned the demographic shifts in the second area make it higher risk. Can you dig a bit deeper into why those shifts specifically correlate with instability? Like, is there a specific reason why a changing population makes the market more volatile compared to a static one?",
